# SEO & meta

Personal brand first. Full titles live in `consts.ts` — `PageLayout` uses them as-is (no `| Rafael Roman` suffix except articles).

## Head.astro

- Default OG image: `SITE.OG_IMAGE` (`/og-default.png`)
- Pass `ogType="article"` + `article={{ publishedTime, tags, author }}` for posts
- JSON-LD via `jsonLd` prop → `JsonLd.astro`

## Schema helpers (`src/lib/seo.ts`)

- Homepage: `personSchema` + `webSiteSchema` in `index.astro`
- Articles: `articleSchema` + `breadcrumbSchema` in `ArticleLayout.astro`

## Draft exclusion

Prod build filters `draft: true` in `[...slug].astro`, RSS, and homepage listings. Sitemap follows built pages only.

## Verify

Inspect built HTML for `application/ld+json`, `og:image`, single `og:type`. Do not rely on `web_fetch` for JSON-LD detection.
